                    "line_text": "La Fayette et Segrais, couple sublime et tendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Le modèle, avant vous, de nos galants écrits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "1"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Des champs élysiens, sur les ailes des Ris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "2"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "D'où ne viendrait-on pas, Sapho, pour vous entendre ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "2"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ils avaient bien raison : quel dieu, charmant auteur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "0"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Quel dieu vous a donné ce langage enchanteur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "3"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ce naturel aisé dont l'art n'approche point ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "4"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sapho, qui ne croirait que l'amour vous inspire ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "5"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mais vous vous contentez de vanter son empire ;",
